node.text:
Faith Counts is thrilled to announce the first Photo Your Faith Contest. It’s simple: take a NEW and ORIGINAL picture that demonstrates your faith in one of 4 categories: 📷 Nature 📸 Home 📷 Sacred Spaces 📸 and Faith in Action, post the photo on Instagram, tag @MyFaithCounts and use hashtag #PhotoYourFaith. Then submit the entry form at faithcounts.com.

You could win $10,000!!

#faith #faithcounts #photoyourfaith #photocontest #photography
